column2: Think of a superpower. For example, going anywhere instantly, travelling in time, reading minds.
Ask your child “If you had the superpower to […] how would you use it?
Encourage them to give themselves a superhero name and act it out.
Now let them choose a super power for you!
Make sure you act it out too! ",,,,,,,,,,,,,,,a6c4f514-47c0-4773-948c-808f8eb1e511,,execute_actions,;
